HEADWORD: Tidife
<hw>Tid"ife</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The blue
titmouse.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The ⟦ldquo⟧tidif⟦rdquo⟧ mentioned in Chaucer is by some
